  "title": "Quantity Surveyor #80336",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Construction</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Quantity Surveyor</strong></li><li>Working Location: Bedok</li><li>Working Hours: Monday - Friday (9.00am – 6.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Source suppliers and subcontractors; obtain and evaluate tender quotations.</li><li>Prepare cost comparisons and pricing summaries.</li><li>Take-off measurements and prepare BOQs, tenders, and quotations.</li><li>Review and evaluate subcontractor/supplier claims and invoices.</li><li>Prepare monthly progress claims.</li><li>Other tasks as assigned by Management.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Quantity Surveying, Building, or equivalent.</li><li>At least 3 years’ relevant experience in the construction industry.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80336 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
